HEADWORD: no-no
<hw>no"-no</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Something improper,
unethical, inadvisable, or illegal; <as>as, salt is a <ex>no-no</ex> for
someone after a heart attack</as>.</def> <mark>[informal]</mark>⟦br⟧
